# About

This is a image that contains the known youtube-dl tool to download videos from
video sites eg. youtube, vimeo.

For documentation see: https://github.com/rg3/youtube-dl/blob/master/README.md#readme

# Important notice

Note that stream ripping or video ripping violates many ToS. Using this is your own
responsibility.

# Usage

$ docker run -it -v /local/output/folder:/media-output matglas/youtube-dl:latest
$ youtube-dl [video url]
